This water

1055
00:43:22,177 --> 00:43:24,577
It watches the spring snow melt

1056
00:43:25,627 --> 00:43:29,627
It guards the home through all seasons

1057
00:43:29,997 --> 00:43:33,127
Drip drop, under the eaves

1058
00:43:33,377 --> 00:43:35,417
This water

1059
00:43:36,057 --> 00:43:38,887
It fills your cup with tea

1060
00:43:39,627 --> 00:43:41,567
It washes away the past

1061
00:43:41,887 --> 00:43:43,877
Every splash

1062
00:43:43,877 --> 00:43:47,397
Is a gesture of love to the world

1063
00:43:47,647 --> 00:43:51,377
Time is like water,
